       capable of performing whatever the work is meant to do.

    b) You must inform the recipient via an interactive
       interface (or other appropriate means) of the circumstances
       and basis of the warranty of the work.

    c) If you conveyed a work in object code form subject to a
       written warranty, the warranty must itself be conveyed in
